# Cursor Rules for Quark Leads

# Architecture
- Always follow the event-driven pipeline: Enrichment -> Classification.
- Use Prisma for all database operations.
- Business logic must stay in Services.

# Testing
- Unit tests go to test/unit/ and use .spec.ts.
- E2E tests go to test/e2e/ and use .e2e.test.ts.

# Standards
- Use Zod for validating any external or AI-generated data.
- Maintain the Hybrid Storage (Relational + JSONB) pattern.
- Follow AGENTS.md for detailed instructions.
